dct_title_s: State of New Jersey Board of Commerce and Navigation Proposed Tunnel Lincoln Highway Crossing Under the Hackensack River between Jersey City & Kearny, N.J.
dct_description_sm: Map depicts the proposed dredging and construction for the Lincoln Highway Tunnel across the Hackensack River between Jersey City and Kearny. No streets are shown.
